%#----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Setup
%#----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Prerequisites:

  * [Ruby] 1.8.6 or newer.

  * [RubyGems] 1.3.6 or newer.

  * [ruby-debug] will be used to help you debug assertion
    failures interactively if it is installed.  Otherwise, the
    standard interactive Ruby shell (IRB) will be used instead.

Installing:

    gem install dfect

Upgrading:

    gem update dfect

Removing:

    gem uninstall dfect
